Next year is <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">the 50th anniversary of <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the United Nations</COREF></COREF> .
Then , <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the United Nations</COREF> will hold various commemorative activities .
