<COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">It</COREF> still possesses quite a number of weaknesses and imperfections .
<COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">The United Nations '</COREF> aim and principles have not been completely adhered to .
<COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Qichen Qian</COREF> pointed out that in recent years with <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">the cold war</COREF> coming to <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> end , unprecedented huge changes have taken place in the international situation , and the pattern of <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">the world</COREF> is being gradually changed in a multipolar direction .
