<COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Qichen Qian</COREF> said that <COREF ID="7" TYPE="IDENT">China</COREF> is an charter member country of <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the United Nations</COREF> and a permanent member of the Security Council and made an important contribution to the birth of <COREF ID="5" TYPE="IDENT">the United Nations</COREF> .
